PropertyBag.Description: Product view for IE based transactions.
PropertyBag.Name: IE

Property.Description: Unit of Measure for this BPC. (Drives conversion routines).
Property.Name: UOM

Property.Description: Date service was used by end user. (Info only) (Always in GMT)
Property.Name: ConsumptionDate

Property.Description: Date the transactions was processed by mediation. (Always in GMT)
Property.Name: ProcessedDate

Property.Description: Guiding date for rating/billing/etc. (Always in GMT)
Property.Name: BillingDate

Property.Description: Service or Point of entry time zone offset.
Property.Name: ServicePOETimeZone

Property.Description: Intial rate used by the system during pipeline processing.
Property.Name: Rate

Property.Description: Percent that the initial rate is adjusted by before use in amount calculation.
Property.Name: FactorDiscountPercent

Property.Description: Percent that AMP adjusts the final transaction by.
Property.Name: AMPDiscountPercent

Property.Description: A UOM is triggered when the transactions UOM is different than the base BPCs. If so, the BPC rating UOM is stored here. If not, the incoming UOM is stored here.
Property.Name: RatingUOM

Property.Description: A UOM is triggered when the transactions UOM is different than the base BPCs. If so, the new rating units are stored here. If not, the incoming units are stored here.
Property.Name: RatingUnits

Property.Description: A UOM is triggered when the transactions UOM is different than the base BPCs. If so, the BPC invoicing UOM is stored here. If not, the incoming UOM is stored here.
Property.Name: InvoicingUOM

Property.Description: A UOM is triggered when the transactions UOM is different than the base BPCs. If so, the new invoicing units are stored here. If not, the incoming units are stored here.
Property.Name: InvoicingUnits

Property.Description: When connect unit processing is executed, the BPC could change.
Property.Name: OriginalBPC

Property.Description: Holds the BPC value prior to the connect unit BPC overlaying it.
Property.Name: PreConnectUnitBPC

Property.Description: 0=No Set; 1=Success; 2=No active rulesset defined; 3=BPC not configured in ruleset
Property.Name: ConnectPackageStatus

Property.Description: If true, all transactions rated at zero will be suppressed from the invoice XML.
Property.Name: SuppressZeroRated

Property.Description: The time the event is deemed to have occurred
Property.Name: Timestamp

Property.Description: The charge assoicated with the event which may summarize other charges within the event.The amount can be negative to represent a credit.
Property.Name: EventCharge

Property.Description: Identifes which MetraView page will present the Event.
Property.Name: PresentationPageId

Property.Description: The EventTax tax for the Event.
Property.Name: EventTax

Property.Description: The FederalTax tax for the Event.
Property.Name: FederalTax

Property.Description: The StateTax tax for the Event.
Property.Name: StateTax

Property.Description: The CountyTax tax for the Event.
Property.Name: CountyTax

Property.Description: The LocalTax tax for the Event.
Property.Name: LocalTax

Property.Description: The OtherTax tax for the Event.
Property.Name: OtherTax
